  "backstory": "Kaelen keeps the old border paths and carries maps no court still admits exist. He learned to follow the broken roads by moonlight, listening for the old ranger bells hidden in hollow trees. Since the crown fell, his patrols have become quieter and more dangerous, but he still marks safe passage for those who travel under honest need."
